# **01  Risk register overview**

All product, technical, market, legal, financial, and operational risks consolidated from DOC-01, DOC-02, DOC-04, DOC-07, DOC-08, DOC-09, and RE-DOC-05. This is the single source of truth for risk tracking. Review at every sprint boundary and before any phase gate.

| **Scoring methodology:** Likelihood: 1 (Very Low) · 2 (Low) · 3 (Medium) · 4 (High) · 5 (Very High) Impact: 1 (Negligible) · 2 (Minor) · 3 (Moderate) · 4 (Major) · 5 (Critical) Score = Likelihood × Impact. Score ≥ 15: Critical (red). Score 8–14: High (orange). Score < 8: Manageable (green). |
| --- |

| **Risk category** | **Count** | **Highest score** | **Owner** |
| --- | --- | --- | --- |
| **Product** | 6 | 16 (R-006 dish database) | Engineering + Content |
| **Technical / RE** | 6 | 25 (R-011 allergen violation) | Engineering |
| **Market / competitive** | 5 | 9 (R-015 competitor entry) | Founder |
| **Legal / compliance** | 5 | 20 (R-020 DPDP gap) | Founder + Legal |
